extensionDescription.message: LinkedIn Container isola tu activitate de LinkedIn del resto de tu activitate web, impediente a LinkedIn de traciar te foras de su sito via cookies de tertios.
extensionDescription.description: Description of the extension. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

in-fbc-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

in-fbc-p1.message: LinkedIn pote ora traciar te sur iste sito. Pro remover iste sito de LinkedIn Container, elige Sitos permittite in LinkedIn Container e remove lo del lista.

on-facebook-subhead.message: Sur LinkedIn o un altere sito includite in LinkedIn Container
on-facebook-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

on-facebook-p1.message: Iste icone appare in le barra de adresse de Firefox quando tu visita sitos gerite per LinkedIn o sitos que tu ha addite a LinkedIn Container.
on-facebook-p1.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

on-facebook-p2.message: Iste sitos debe acceder a tu identitate de LinkedIn (o saper qui tu es) pro poter functionar. Isto significa etiam que LinkedIn pote traciar tote lo que tu face sur iste sitos.
on-facebook-p2.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop up when the user is on LinkedIn.

notOnLinkedInHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

notOnLinkedInText.message: Iste sito es foras de LinkedIn Container. Isto rende plus difficile pro LinkedIn traciar te sur le web.
notOnLinkedInText.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

onUnknownSiteHeader.message: Iste sito non es in LinkedIn Container.
onUnknownSiteHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on an "unknown" website - e.g., about:newtab. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

facebookContainer.description: This is the name of the extension, and appears at the top of all onboarding panels. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container".

onboarding1-subhead.description: This is the subhead of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding1-p1.message: LinkedIn pote traciar tu navigation ben ultra LinkedIn.com. Per exemplo, le buttones "Me place" e "Compartir" de LinkedIn pote traciar le paginas que tu visita — mesmo paginas que tu non ha jammais compartite o marcate como "Me place".
onboarding1-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding1-p2.message: LinkedIn Container crea un barriera inter le sitos de LinkedIn e le resto del web, rendente plus difficile pro LinkedIn traciar te in linea.

onboarding2-subhead.message: Sur LinkedIn o un altere sito includite in LinkedIn Container
onboarding2-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding2-alt.message: Le icone de barriera de LinkedIn Container
onboarding2-alt.description: This is alternative text for the icon in the second onboarding panel

onboarding2-p1.message: Iste icone appare in le barra de adresse de Firefox quando tu visita sitos includite in LinkedIn Container, como LinkedIn.com.
onboarding2-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the second onboarding panel.

onboarding2-p2.message: Iste sitos debe acceder a tu identitate de LinkedIn (o saper qui tu es) pro poter functionar. Isto significa etiam que LinkedIn pote traciar tote lo que tu face sur iste sitos.
onboarding2-p2.description: This is the second paragraph of the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding4-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-p1.message: Mesmo si tu non es sur LinkedIn, LinkedIn pote traciar te in linea. Le buttones que te permitte publicar cosas sur LinkedIn o aperir session in sitos web con tu conto LinkedIn contine traciatores. LinkedIn Container bloca iste traciatores e monstra le icone de barriera pro monstrar te ubi le traciatores ha essite removite.
onboarding4-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-img.message: Iste imagine monstra como le icone de barriera de LinkedIn Container appare sur le pagina al latere de un button “Me place” de LinkedIn.
onboarding4-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-subhead.message: Aperir session con LinkedIn sur altere sitos
onboarding5-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-p1.message: Pro usar tu conto LinkedIn sur altere sitos, tu debe placiar iste sitos in le contentor. Clicca sur le icone de barriera e clicca sur “Permitter sito in LinkedIn Container” in basso.
onboarding5-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-img.message: Iste imagine monstra como le button pro adder un sito a LinkedIn Container appare in le pannello.
onboarding5-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-p2.message: Isto permitte aperir session con LinkedIn, ma etiam permitte que LinkedIn tracia tu activitate sur iste sito.
onboarding5-p2.description: This is the second paragraph on the fifth onboarding panel.

btn-allow.description: This is a button to allows users to whitelist the domain, adding it to the LinkedIn container.

btn-cancel.description: This is a button to cancel out of the onboarding panel.

btn-next.description: This is a button to continue to the next onboarding panel.

btn-back.description: This is a button that returns the user to the previous onboarding panel.

btn-done.description: This is a button the user clicks to close out the panel when they have finished reading the text.

btn-arrow-back.description: This is alternative text for the back arrow button.

btn-arrow-forward.message: Ir a Como functiona LinkedIn Container
btn-arrow-forward.description: This is alternative text for the arrow icon next to the "How LinkedIn Container Works" link

no-trackers-p1.message: LinkedIn Container non ha detegite traciatores de LinkedIn sur iste pagina. Nonobstante, le pagina poterea continer altere typos de traciatores.

learn-more.description: This is a link that opens a page with more information about LinkedIn Container.

how-fbc-works.description: This is a button that opens the LinkedIn Container onboarding flow.

trackers-detected-subhead.message: Nos te ha protegite de LinkedIn.
trackers-detected-subhead.description: This is a subhead, and it means that the add on has protected the user by blocking LinkedIn trackers.

trackers-detected-p1.message: Le buttones de LinkedIn que appare sur sitos de compras, novas, etc. contine traciatores que divulga a LinkedIn ubi tu ha essite sur le web. Mesmo si tu non usa jammais iste buttones "Me place" o "Compartir", le traciatores pote totevia colliger datos sur tu navigation. LinkedIn Container bloca iste traciatores.

trackers-detected-p2.message: LinkedIn Container bloca iste traciatores. Nonobstante, si tu clicca sur alcun de iste buttones, LinkedIn potera traciar te.

trackers-detected-fence-alt.message: Barriera de LinkedIn Container con scuto.
trackers-detected-fence-alt.description: This is alternative text describing the container fence icon.

sites-included.description: This is a header for the list of websites that are in the LinkedIn Container by default. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the language.

no-sites-added.description: This message is shown beneath the 'SITES YOU’VE ALLOWED' list header when no sites have been added to the contaner.

sites-allowed.description: This is the header for the list of sites the user has manually added into the LinkedIn Container. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the lanaguage.

sites-added-p1.message: LinkedIn Container confina le sitos pertinente a LinkedIn in un zona delimitate. Tu pote permitter que altere sitos entra in iste zona, ma isto permittera a LinkedIn de traciar plus de tu navigation web.

button-allow-site.description: Button text that allows sites to be added to the LinkedIn Container

button-remove-site.description: Button text that removes an already-added site from the LinkedIn Container to the default container

button-remove-site-tooltip.message: Iste sito pertine a LinkedIn, dunque non pote esser removite de LinkedIn Container.
button-remove-site-tooltip.description: Tooltip that is displayed when hovering over the remove site button

remove-site-subhead.message: Remover iste sito ab LinkedIn Container?

remove-site-p1.message: Si tu remove iste sito ab LinkedIn Container, le function de aperir session con LinkedIn non functionara plus e le cookies de traciamento de LinkedIn essera delite.

remove-site-p2.message: Si tu vole aperir session con LinkedIn de novo, tu debe re-includer le sito in LinkedIn Container.

add-site-subhead.message: Permitter a LinkedIn de traciar te sur iste sito?

add-site-p1.message: Isto te permitte aperir session con LinkedIn, ma permitte a LinkedIn de sequer lo que tu face sur iste sito.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share.message: LinkedIn Container ha disactivate iste button e ha blocate a LinkedIn de traciar tu visita a iste pagina.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-login.message: LinkedIn Container ha blocate traciatores de LinkedIn. Si tu aperi session con LinkedIn sur iste sito, LinkedIn potera traciar te.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p1.message: Permitter que LinkedIn te tracia hic?

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p2.message: Si tu aperi session con LinkedIn, alora LinkedIn potera traciar tu activitate sur iste sito. Isto pote adjutar les a elaborar un imagine plus complete de tu vita in linea.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-checkbox.message: Non monstrar me isto de novo

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share-passive.message: Si tu clicca sur iste button, LinkedIn potera traciar tu activitate sur iste sito.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-email.message: Si tu usa tu real adresse e-mail hic, LinkedIn pote traciar te. Clicca pro saper plus.

inPageUI-tooltip-email-prompt-p1.message: Permitte tu a LinkedIn de traciar te hic?

inPageUI-tooltip-email-prompt-p2.message: Iste sito pote compartir tu adresse de e-mail con LinkedIn, lo que permitte a LinkedIn de traciar te. Usa un servicio como Firefox Relay pro celar tu adresse de e-mail real.
